From 0cc268d5ca3669f0c5fecdee7cbf9a34d3922801 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Sat, 6 Jun 2026 16:53:32 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat: service control panel, custom packages, health
 monitoring, feature access guards

- Add Prisma models: ServiceDefinition, TenantService, CustomPackage, ServiceHealthLog
- Add includedServices[] to Plan model; run service_control migration
- Seed 29 service definitions across 7 categories with core flags; add Custom plan
- Create syncTenantServices utility called on tenant create & plan change
- Fix super-admin plan PUT/POST handlers with explicit type conversions
- Add SuperAdmin routes: services CRUD, health check, company service overrides, custom packages
- Add dashboard/service-status and settings/my-services API routes
- New SuperAdminServices page with global toggle, maintenance mode, health monitor (60s poll)
- New SuperAdminCustomPackage page with checkbox grid, live preview, package builder
- SuperAdminPlans: tag input for features array, checkbox grid for includedServices
- SuperAdminCompanies: Services tab with per-tenant toggle, override badge, reset to defaults
- SuperAdminDashboard: Pending custom package requests widget with Configure links
- SignupPage: Custom Package option with custom success message
- AppLayout: dismissible maintenance banners fetched on load (sessionStorage dismiss)
- DashboardPage: System Status widget showing all service health indicators
- useServiceEnabled hook + ServiceDisabledPlaceholder component
- Feature guards on WhatsApp, Automation, Integrations pages

